item.title: CVE-2017-2226|2024-08-05T13:48:05.073Z -- national%20tax%20agency -- setup%20file%20of%20advance%20preparation%20for%20e-tax%20software%20%28web%20version%29
item.description: Untrusted search path vulnerability in Setup file of advance preparation for e-Tax software (WEB version) (1.17.1) and earlier allows an attacker to gain privileges via a Trojan horse DLL in an unspecified directory.

item.title: CVE-2017-2215|2024-08-05T13:48:04.309Z -- national%20tax%20agency -- installer%20of%20%22setup%20file%20of%20advance%20preparation%22%20%28jizen_setup.exe%29
item.description: Untrusted search path vulnerability in Installer of "Setup file of advance preparation" (jizen_setup.exe) (The version which was available on the website prior to 2017 June 12) allows an attacker to gain privileges via a Trojan horse DLL in an unspecified directory.
